<para><anchor id="index_1md__2home_2loic_2EPITECH_2rtype_2Mystic-Type_2README"/> Multiplayer R-Type-like with an authoritative TCP/UDP server and a raylib graphical client.</para>
<sect1 id="index_1autotoc_md1">
<title>Prerequisites</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>CMake ≥ 3.14</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>C++17 compiler</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>raylib (fetched automatically via FetchContent)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Works on macOS, Linux, and Windows (WSA init handled in entry points).</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="index_1autotoc_md2">
<title>Build</title>
<sect2 id="index_1autotoc_md3">
<title>Linux</title>
<para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">./build.sh<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#<sp/>build<sp/>client<sp/>+<sp/>servers</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> Executables are in <computeroutput>build/linux/</computeroutput>:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>rtype-tcp-server</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>rtype-udp-server</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>rtype-client</computeroutput></para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="index_1autotoc_md4">
<title>macOS</title>
<para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>-S<sp/>.<sp/>-B<sp/>build<sp/>-G<sp/>&quot;Unix<sp/>Makefiles&quot;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>--build<sp/>build</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> Executables are in <computeroutput>build/</computeroutput>:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>rtype-tcp-server</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>rtype-udp-server</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>rtype-client</computeroutput></para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="index_1autotoc_md5">
